Privacy Policy for Prediction Bot
Effective Date: 9/30/2024

This Privacy Policy explains how Prediction Bot ("we," "us," or "our") collects, uses, and protects your information when you use our bot on Discord. By using Prediction Bot, you agree to the collection and use of information in accordance with this policy.

1. Information We Collect
When you use Prediction Bot, we may collect the following types of information:

1.1 User Data
User IDs: We collect your Discord user ID to provide personalized services and maintain user interactions.
Server IDs: We collect server IDs to operate effectively within specific Discord servers.
Usernames: We collect usernames to output leaderboard information
Server Names: We collect server names to personlize support experiences.
1.2 Interaction Data
Commands Used: We log the commands you use to improve our services and understand user preferences.
Command Arguments: We store command arguments to store in progress prediction data.
Embed Content: We store embed IDs to be able to interact with the embeds on the fly.
2. How We Use Your Information
We may use the information we collect for various purposes, including:

To provide and maintain Prediction Bot's functionality.
To improve our bot and develop new features.
To respond to user inquiries and provide customer support.
To monitor usage and analyze trends.
3. Data Retention
We retain your information only for as long as necessary to provide our services and fulfill the purposes outlined in this Privacy Policy. If you wish to have your data deleted, please contact us.

4. Data Sharing and Disclosure
We do not sell, trade, or otherwise transfer your personal information to third parties without your consent, except in the following situations:

Legal Compliance: We may disclose your information if required to do so by law or in response to valid requests by public authorities.
Protection of Rights: We may disclose your information to protect our rights, privacy, safety, or property, or that of others.
5. Security of Your Information
We take the security of your information seriously and implement reasonable measures to protect it from unauthorized access, disclosure, alteration, or destruction. However, no method of transmission over the Internet or method of electronic storage is 100% secure.

6. Your Rights
Depending on your location, you may have the following rights regarding your personal information:

The right to access the data we hold about you.
The right to request corrections to your personal information.
The right to request deletion of your personal information.
The right to withdraw consent for data processing.
To exercise these rights, please contact us using the information below.

7. Changes to This Privacy Policy
We may update our Privacy Policy from time to time. We will notify you of any changes by posting the new Privacy Policy in the bot or through Discord announcements. You are advised to review this Privacy Policy periodically for any changes.

8. Contact Us
If you have any questions or concerns about this Privacy Policy, please contact us at https://discord.gg/ZGvbvcdh.
